{"type": "article", "id": 10442, "title": "Awair 智能空气质量检测仪", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-05T07:14:44Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702125802lOCGXdcK7WiEJYuU.png", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">这是一款名为 “Awair” 的智能空气质量检测仪器，除了普通的空气监测，Awair 可以通过对温度，湿度，气体，颗粒等指标的分析，对空气质量对健康的影响提出解决方案，并提出简单的建议，如开窗或饮用蜂蜜水。仪器有过敏，美容，睡眠等 6 个预设选项，选择不同的情景，Awair 都可以给出不同的解决方案。目前售价 150 美元起，<a href=\"https://getawair.com/\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021257589zWmOw0SNHjkZhTt.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.46111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021257590jHnfqRzoZWdul98.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.52685185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125759MviBEGFA1a7jqQru.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.72727273\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125800DL6msEhkNzH5PSUf.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.67307692\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125800gfH8YK64QTDl5oOx.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.68105516\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125801QiWB5UvAEyxf8HMr.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.8037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span>\r\n</p>\n\n"}